<2ND_LINE>AM-Reagan-Byrd-Summit,580</2ND_LINE>
<HEAD>Reagan Says Moscow Summit Sewed Seeds of Greater Trust</HEAD>
<NOTE>EDs: Retransmits a0606 to fix slugline</NOTE>
<BYLINE>By W. DALE NELSON</BYLINE>
